raja narasimha ( kannada : ರಾಜ &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 2003 indian kannada romantic drama - action film directed by muthyala subbaiah and written by posani krishna murali . the film stars vishnuvardhan along with ramya krishnan and raasi in the prominent roles . the film was produced by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; under the sri &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; productions banner . the film released on 21 march 2003 to generally positive reviews from critics . however , the film failed commercially at the box office . the same story was remade in telugu as palnati &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and released in the same year . the film starred nandamuri balakrishna , arti agarwal and sonali bendre .